ads to mark. Marks affect each head separately. A head that is not marked ignores the mark’s effects and does not trigger effects tied to the mark. Other effects and conditions, such as dazed or stunned, apply to all of the heads.</p></tr></td><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Triple Actions&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Calastryx acts three times in a round, once for each head, on initiative counts 30, 20, and 10. It has a full set of actions on each turn and cannot delay or ready actions. It can use one immediate action between each turn.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Triple Actions</b></p><p>Calastryx acts three times in a round, once for each head, on initiative counts 30, 20, and 10. It has a full set of actions on each turn and cannot delay or ready actions. It can use one immediate action between each turn.</p></tr></td><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Power of Three&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each of Calastryx’s heads tracks the use of encounter and recharge actions separately. Each head has a full array of the listed powers.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Power of Three</b></p><p>Each of Calastryx’s heads tracks the use of encounter and recharge actions separately. Each head has a full array of the listed powers.</p></tr></td><tr><td><p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\">[[/roll 0#&lt;p style=\"background-color:green;color:white;\"&gt; &lt;b&gt;Bloodied Birth&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The first time Calastryx is bloodied, it sprouts a fourth head. That head has its own separate set of encounter and recharge powers. Its initiative is 40.&lt;/p&gt;]]  <b>Bloodied Birth</b></p><p>The first time Calastryx is bloodied, it sprouts a fourth head. That head has its own separate set of encounter and recharge powers. Its initiative is 40.</p></tr></td></table>",
